long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Your Clear Thinking is Valuable

FleetMarks is your everyday extension for Surfing Internet.

Turning Ordinary Moments into Extraordinary Results

Whether you're a Developer, Teacher, or a Home Automation Hacker...

FleetMarks is a excellent bookmarks category manager that optimizes categorize the bookmarks your collected all over the internet and significantly improved bookmarks searching, analyzing experience!

Just click the hexagram at right corner to save page.

► New clean layout for optimal manage bookmarks
► Easy to searching bookmarks in address bar
► Convenient add tags as you want
► Convenient view bookmarks category in options page
► Quick preview when hovering over node
► Detail preview when click node
► Dozens of other improvements

Like FleetMarks? Please rate us ★★★★★

Q: How do I use FleetMarks?
A: Just install our extension and keep viewing website as usual. The FleetMarks will automatically save page every time you click the hexagram on the top-right corner.

Q: How does it work?
A: It's simple. The extension replaces bookmarks_bar folder to all tags with it's child folder as tag on FleetMarks. 

Q: Why am I use FleetMarks?
A: In my personal experience, the chrome origin bookmarks manager not good enough for tag bookmarks.
